genresAdvancedInfo.name: musique pour enfant quebecois
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Musique pour enfant quebecois is a music genre for children in Quebec, Canada. It is characterized by a mix of traditional folk music and modern pop music. The lyrics are often educational and focus on topics such as history, geography, and social values. The music is upbeat and fun, with catchy melodies and sing-along choruses.
